quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  6,36,Innamā Yastajību Al-Ladhīna Yasma`ūna Wa Al-Mawtá Yab`athuhumu Allāhu Thumma 'Ilayhi Yurja`ūna
  6,37,Wa Qālū Lawlā Nuzzila `Alayhi 'Āyatun Min Rabbihi Qul 'Inna Allāha Qādirun `Alá 'An Yunazzila 'Āyatan Wa Lakinna 'Aktharahum Lā Ya`lamūna
  6,38,Wa Mā Min Dābbatin Fī Al-'Arđi Wa Lā Ţā'irin Yaţīru Bijanāĥayhi 'Illā 'Umamun 'Amthālukum Mā Farraţnā Fī Al-Kitābi Min Shay'in Thumma 'Ilá Rabbihim Yuĥsharūna
  6,39,Wa Al-Ladhīna Kadhabū Bi'āyātinā Şummun Wa Bukmun Fī Až-Žulumāti Man Yasha'i Allāhu Yuđlilhu Wa Man Yasha' Yaj`alhu `Alá Şirāţin Mustaqīmin
  6,40,Qul 'Ara'aytakum 'In 'Atākum `Adhābu Allāhi 'Aw 'Atatkumu As-Sā`atu 'Aghayra Allāhi Tad`ūna 'In Kuntum Şādiqīna
  6,41,Bal 'Īyāhu Tad`ūna Fayakshifu Mā Tad`ūna 'Ilayhi 'In Shā'a Wa Tansawna Mā Tushrikūna
  6,42,Wa Laqad 'Arsalnā 'Ilá 'Umamin Min Qablika Fa'akhadhnāhum Bil-Ba'sā'i Wa Ađ-Đarrā'i La`allahum Yatađarra`ūna
  6,43,Falawlā 'Idh Jā'ahum Ba'sunā Tađarra`ū Wa Lakin Qasat Qulūbuhum Wa Zayyana Lahumu Ash-Shayţānu Mā Kānū Ya`malūn
  6,44,Falammā Nasū Mā Dhukkirū Bihi Fataĥnā `Alayhim 'Abwāba Kulli Shay'in Ĥattá 'Idhā Fariĥū Bimā 'Ūtū 'Akhadhnāhum Baghtatan Fa'idhā Hum Mublisūna
  6,45,Faquţi`a Dābiru Al-Qawmi Al-Ladhīna Žalamū Wa Al-Ĥamdu Lillāhi Rabbi Al-`Ālamīna
  6,46,Qul 'Ara'aytum 'In 'Akhadha Allāhu Sam`akum Wa 'Abşārakum Wa Khatama `Alá Qulūbikum Man 'Ilahun Ghayru Allāhi Ya'tīkum Bihi Anžur Kayfa Nuşarrifu Al-'Āyāti Thumma Hum Yaşdifūna
  6,47,Qul 'Ara'aytakum 'In 'Atākum `Adhābu Allāhi Baghtatan 'Aw Jahratan Hal Yuhlaku 'Illā Al-Qawmu Až-Žālimūna
  6,48,Wa Mā Nursilu Al-Mursalīna 'Illā Mubashirīna Wa Mundhirīna Faman 'Āmana Wa 'Aşlaĥa Falā Khawfun `Alayhim Wa Lā Hum Yaĥzanūna
  6,49,Wa Al-Ladhīna Kadhabū Bi'āyātinā Yamassuhumu Al-`Adhābu Bimā Kānū Yafsuqūna
  6,50,Qul Lā 'Aqūlu Lakum `Indī Khazā'inu Allāhi Wa Lā 'A`lamu Al-Ghayba Wa Lā 'Aqūlu Lakum 'Innī Malakun 'In 'Attabi`u 'Illā Mā Yūĥá 'Ilayya Qul Hal Yastawī Al-'A`má Wa Al-Başīru 'Afalā Tatafakkarūna
  6,51,Wa 'Andhir Bihi Al-Ladhīna Yakhāfūna 'An Yuĥsharū 'Ilá Rabbihim Laysa Lahum Min Dūnihi Wa Līyun Wa Lā Shafī`un La`allahum Yattaqūna
  6,52,Wa Lā Taţrudi Al-Ladhīna Yad`ūna Rabbahum Bil-Ghadāati Wa Al-`Ashīyi Yurīdūna Wajhahu Mā `Alayka Min Ĥisābihim Min Shay'in Wa Mā Min Ĥisābika `Alayhim Min Shay'in Fataţrudahum Fatakūna Mina Až-Žālimīna
  6,53,Wa Kadhalika Fatannā Ba`đahum Biba`đin Liyaqūlū 'Ahā'uulā' Manna Allāhu `Alayhim Min Bayninā 'Alaysa Allāhu Bi'a`lama Bish-Shākirīna
  6,54,Wa 'Idhā Jā'aka Al-Ladhīna Yu'uminūna Bi'āyātinā Faqul Salāmun `Alaykum Kataba Rabbukum `Alá Nafsihi Ar-Raĥmata 'Annahu Man `Amila Minkum Sū'āan Bijahālatin Thumma Tāba Min Ba`dihi Wa 'Aşlaĥa Fa'annahu Ghafūrun Raĥīmun
  6,55,Wa Kadhalika Nufaşşilu Al-'Āyāti Wa Litastabīna Sabīlu Al-Mujrimīna
  6,56,Qul 'Innī Nuhītu 'An 'A`buda Al-Ladhīna Tad`ūna Min Dūni Allāhi Qul Lā 'Attabi`u 'Ahwā'akum Qad Đalaltu 'Idhāan Wa Mā 'Anā Mina Al-Muhtadīna
  6,57,Qul 'Innī `Alá Bayyinatin Min Rabbī Wa Kadhabtum Bihi Mā `Indī Mā Tasta`jilūna Bihi 'Ini Al-Ĥukmu 'Illā Lillāhi Yaquşşu Al-Ĥaqqa Wa Huwa Khayru Al-Fāşilīna
  6,58,Qul Law 'Anna `Indī Mā Tasta`jilūna Bihi Laquđiya Al-'Amru Baynī Wa Baynakum Wa Allāhu 'A`lamu Biž-Žālimīna